    veganOptions: "yes", glutenFreeOptions: "yes", halalOptions: "yes",
    description: "Dishoom is a phenomenon and families are a huge part of its appeal. The all-day Bombay café format means breakfast, lunch, or dinner — the bacon naan at breakfast is the stuff of London legend. The kids menu is genuinely excellent (not just 'mild curry'), and the atmospheric Irani café setting fascinates children. Staff are consistently praised for their warmth with young diners. Queue for breakfast on weekends or book for lunch.",
